Package edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.data

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.data.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable, java.lang.Comparable<Student>

    public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Student>, Identifiable
    This class contains the Student objects that will be used for the use of the sorting algorithms based a student's information, such as first name, last name, id, credit hours, GPA, and Unity Id.
    Author:
    Bilal Mohamad
